Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:02.69,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:05.86,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:08.76,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:12.03,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today's case is the continuation\Nof a reunion murder case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.43,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Let's listen to "Mune ga doki-doki"\Nas we review the last episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:39.08,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The old man's college buddies had a reunion at the hot spring resort, "Benkei".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:42.25,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The attendees were the club manager, Yumi Horikoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:45.55,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}the model shop owner, Jun Omura,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:48.42,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}the high school gym instructor, Yukio Ayashiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.03,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}his wife, Noriko Ayashiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:54.03,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}the Chiba Prefectural police detective, Kazushi Nakamichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:57.07,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and then me, Ran, and the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.23,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We went to wake up Yumi Horikoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:02.84,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}who was still in her room after the fireworks show ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.01,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}only to find that she had committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:08.01,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}by shooting herself in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:12.55,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A makeshift autopsy showed that she had died seven hours earlier—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.98,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}at around 3:00 PM, when everyone was playing ping-pong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:18.35,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}before leaving for the fireworks show!
