Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:29.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she did say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.47,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I really wish I were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:35.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've been serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:39.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how did Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0} shoot herself in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask strange questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:48.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She put the gun up to her head like so and—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Mouri! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Nakamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally when someone commits suicide with a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they stick the barrel against their head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:02.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then her bullet wound is missing something vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Burn marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you shoot a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a stream of hot air accompanies the bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you shoot with the gun against your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have to leave burn marks behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that there are none here means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:29.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...that someone else shot her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone shot her and then tried to make it look like a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone in this inn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:50.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think one of us did it, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:56.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said the murder took place at approximately 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was right after she went off on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:02.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all in the ping-pong room from 3:00 to 6:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so none of us could have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only time someone left
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was when Omura went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was well past 5:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he came back in less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have done it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then it was an outside job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the killer could have gone anywhere along the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,plus the door wasn't locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:36.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very conceivable that someone entered from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:39.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, let's hear what the employees have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone might've seen a suspicious character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:05:01.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all out to lunch at three o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:05.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and even after we came back, there was no one that suspicious—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Actually, there was such a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What were they like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A young lass with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:17.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed very distraught and rushed straight upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you describe this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's right there behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was those two young'uns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:30.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that was around 6:30, just when the fireworks started...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's talking about when we came to wake Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0} up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she wouldn't miss the fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:40.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to her room and were about to go in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...I stopped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets grumpy when people wake her up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured it best that they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:50.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamichi? You were still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I had worked up a sweat playing ping-pong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I took a quick dip in the public bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:01.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt bad for making you and Omura go on ahead and save our spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you two were taking a bath too, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:08.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We were in the open-air bath, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:14.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had gone to wake her up, she might still be—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi died while we were playin' ping-pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We would've been too late no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:25.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Omura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:32.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting strange since this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come clean! What're you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I left to go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I saw Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was after 5:00 when you went to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi was already dead by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her even though she was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:01.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was glaring at the ping-pong room from an upstairs window!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:04.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! Yumi was already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:12.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if what I actually saw was her... her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:19.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious! There's no such thing as ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mind was just confused because you were tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just imagining things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:32.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen at our inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this about ghosts and dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:38.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:41.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they need medical treatment right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:46.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are on their way as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Wait a minute! That's strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:52.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Why did that person say that at that time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:57.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the murderer is one of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:59.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer was someone else! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Where are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:05.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamichi! You're in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:07.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta use the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:15.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, isn't it too early to tell that this was an outside job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the way Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0} was killed was—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:26.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! I don't need any of your babbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was no outside job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone who snuck in from outside
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:33.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,kill somebody and make it look like a suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was an inside job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it was one of my best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why or how they did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:46.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't let them get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:49.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll expose them for what they are! This I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:01.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}One of those four is the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No, l have a good idea who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:08.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}lt's most likely the person who said that one odd thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But that person has a perfect alibi—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Ping-Pong Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:14.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}they were in the ping-pong room with everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}l checked Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s estimated time of death for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so that can't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:23.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ln which case, how did that person kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What bothers me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:26.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}is the fact that Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s finger wasn't on the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}of the gun placed in her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You would expect the killer to put her finger on it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}to fake her suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:35.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}lt also bothers me that she didn't have any undergarments on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:39.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and that she had changed into a large yukata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:42.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Did the killer change her clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Benkei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:00.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that's the name of this inn, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact all these arrows are stuck in him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,must mean this is from when Benkei died standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Died standing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Benkei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer used this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I've finally figured out the trick the killer used!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll just put the old man to sleep like always
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}with my Anesthetic Watch Gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.10,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This was an inside job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:52.57,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}In other words, it was one of my best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:56.34,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I won't let them get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.57,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll expose them for what they are! This I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:07.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Understood, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:10.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did the killer shoot her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the killer came to steal her things
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but shot her when she spotted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't we hear the shot when we were playing ping-pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:27.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The killer has to be in here, so why do they all have alibis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Judging from the state of her rigor mortis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yumi's estimated time of death was around 3:00 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:36.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Which means she was murdered immediately after she left us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and returned to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:42.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The rest of us were in the ping-pong room from 3:00 to 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Nobody had the chance to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:48.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What bothers me is what Omura said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.12,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's just it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.79,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I saw her even though she was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.90,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}She was glaring at the ping-pong room from an upstairs window!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Omura went to the bathroom just after 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yumi couldn't have been alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:05.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So why did Omura say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play ping-pong! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! What are you saying at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My shakehand grip is pretty good, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0} used the shakehand grip too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:29.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? She was holding a racket with a shakehand-style in that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:35.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you can't play right now! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have to change clothes if I got all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sweat? Change clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shakehand grip?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:49.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Come to think of it, Yumi had changed into a large yukata...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And had nothing on underneath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And her right index finger stuck out stiffly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}instead of being on the trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}With the shakehand grip,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:02.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}you hold the racket with your index finger out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:05.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Could Yumi have been playing ping-pong with the murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}before she was killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:11.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's ridiculous. What purpose would that serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:17.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I could swear they mentioned something at the police academy—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:22.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, didn't Benkei die while standing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:27.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Benkei fought hordes of enemies off all by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:30.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then died on his feet when they showered him with arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:34.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:39.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mouri. What's the shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:44.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally figured out who killed Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:48.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who killed Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:00.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who killed Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:03.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nakamichi killed her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop joking around...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the ping-pong room with everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,at her estimated time of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your alibi is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:16.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming she really was killed at 3:00 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:21.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? We checked her time of death together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:26.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi's toes were indeed beginning to stiffen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:31.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I estimated that she had died over seven hours prior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are exceptions:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:37.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sudden deaths during intense physical exertion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:41.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In such situations, intramuscular proteins harden more easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:45.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,causing rigor mortis to take effect much more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:50.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just like the heroic Musashibo Benkei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:54.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Benkei's death while standing up—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's been medically proven
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:15:00.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that it's possible to die while standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:03.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. The body was in Yumi's own room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of exercise are you saying I made her do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:12.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she wasn't forced to exert herself in her room—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it was in the ping-pong room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:18.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You made her play ping-pong right up until you killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:21.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were most likely supposed to meet her all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in the ping-pong room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:27.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then you invited us all into the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:30.81,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh yeah! What do you say we play some ping-pong now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.48,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.92,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, Yumi grew angry and returned to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:40.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After 6:00, when everyone had left,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:44.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi went by herself to the ping-pong room, where you were waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been quite the secret rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:50.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You then invited her to a game of ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After making her exert herself for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you got her to return to her room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:07.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...at which point you shot her in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:13.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All to skew the estimated time of death and create the perfect alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You likely used Yumi's short temper to your advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to get her to return to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:25.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi rushed back to her room still holding the racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why her right hand which held the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,had stiffened in the shakehand grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:34.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Yumi I saw right after 5:00 was—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the real Yumi, in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was still alive then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was watching the ping-pong room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:43.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from the 2nd floor and waiting for Nakamichi to be all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi was probably really murdered at 6:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:48.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when the fireworks show started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:52.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The gunshot would seem inconspicuous with all the fireworks exploding about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:57.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nakamichi still had the job
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:17:01.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of wiping off the body's sweat and changing the clothes—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a chance the trick could be discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we learned that she had been sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He had no choice but to remove her undergarments,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he did change her yukata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:14.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a spare one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:18.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the middle of his work, an unforeseen obstacle appeared:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:22.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran and Conan, who came to wake Yumi up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped your work halfway through,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:28.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,exited onto the roof through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and stopped Ran from entering the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You then went with everyone to see the fireworks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:39.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,pretended to get separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:42.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and finished the rest of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:47.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when you put the gun in her hand to make it look like a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it would seem that her hand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:53.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,had already stiffened into that peculiar grip,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:57.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,making it impossible to put her finger on the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:00.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your theory is indeed interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you have any proof that I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person besides me who could've pulled that off
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was you, a police detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:13.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See! You could've done it as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:17.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, anybody could learn that from a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are dumb, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This great policeman couldn't possibly be the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:35.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew that Yumi-{\i1}san{\i0} was dead just by seeing her covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:41.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the following without ever touching Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.24,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.14,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:47.31,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Nobody but me and Mouri are to come in here, since we're detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason you called not for an ambulance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:56.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that it was too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We went out for 18 years, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I met someone half a year ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:16.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this because she would hinder your marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why didn't you marry her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I proposed to her many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But her answer was always no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For 18 long years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:34.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I was about to marry someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi told me this:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.46,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:41.76,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I won't allow you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:46.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when her threatening letters and phone calls
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to my fiancée started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:53.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally she said she was going to send photos of just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her that if she brought the photos to the reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:59.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would buy them all off of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:03.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the day you caught the bank robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:06.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had just met with Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was struggling over what to do about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:15.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the robber's gun fell nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:20.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that I thought up this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal was to take place in the ping-pong room,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:25.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but then I told her this:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:28.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The photos have been removed from your things."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:30.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:33.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why Yumi rushed back to her room,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:35.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,racket still in hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you followed behind and shot her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:43.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot the demon who screwed up my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one was the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:45.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:54.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}...how a murderer feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}...no matter what the reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:03.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I don't want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:08.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you're still as strong as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:12.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. You've just gotten weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Both your mind and your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:07.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been pretty glum lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:12.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame him; those were his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:14.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, if he's that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:16.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't he ever win any matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:19.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, in actual matches he gets so tense
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:23.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that he can't concentrate his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:25.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So he had a knack for being outdone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:28.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go try to cheer him up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:29.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:33.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back to normal eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:45.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This time it's pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:24:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(137,105)\fnSegoe\fscx105\fs28\fsp1\shad0\bord0\alpha&H1F&}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:24:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,395)\fnSegoe\fscx105\fs28\fsp1\shad0\bord0\alpha&H1F&}Next episode's hint right after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.18,0:23:54.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Inspector Megure! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:23:56.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okida's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:58.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's damp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:01.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone who died while sweating, there's too much here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:04.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}lf his heart attack was intentionally caused,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:06.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}then Tokito-{\i1}san{\i0} is the prime suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:10.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But how exactly could he have done it?!
