Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:17.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,234)\a6\fscx100\fscy100\fnDINk\c&HFFFFFF&\b0\fs36\bord0\shad0}The Computer Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:22.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:27.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,430)\fnSegoe\fscx100\bord0\shad0\fs24}Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:25.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time, it's a fight with a computer!
